				<text><![CDATA[<font size='4' color='#004280'><b>REPORT</b></font><br><font size='2' color='#004280'>SELF-ASSESSMENT SURVEY<br><font size='1' color='#004280'>FFPE Tissue - Part 1: Isolated RNA (Version 3 - Draft - V20200506)</font>]]></text>
