				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[Lower storage temp. (2-8Â°C, -20Â°C) slow down the RNA degeneration process. If FFPE tissue is not stored dry, the RNA degradation can increase, and fungal and bacterial growth can be stimulated.]]></text>
			</staticText>
		</band>
