		<band height="78">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement positionType="Float" x="25" y="0" width="545" height="78" uuid="c5346fb9-9a83-4b1b-af1b-2f0c6b8fa7f8"/>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" verticalAlignment="Middle" markup="html">
					<font size="12" pdfFontName="net/sf/jasperreports/fonts/dejavu/DejaVuSerif-Italic.ttf" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[The use of products from different manufacturers can compromise results as the products may not be compatible. They should be used for diagnostic testing only if the components have been tested together and validated to work satisfactorily.]]></text>
			</staticText>
		</band>
		<band height="46">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement positionType="Float" x="25" y="0" width="545" height="46" uuid="0ae50220-3c92-43f5-9f1e-55dda8f7be7c"/>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" verticalAlignment="Middle" markup="html">
					<font size="12" pdfFontName="net/sf/jasperreports/fonts/dejavu/DejaVuSerif-Italic.ttf" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[RNA isolation procedure for FFPE tissue sections should contain the following steps:]]></text>
			</staticText>
		</band>
		<band height="52" splitType="Prevent">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="25" y="0" width="272" height="52" uuid="03cec87e-9cf7-4a29-84e7-b0b74a188b12"/>
				<textElement verticalAlignment="Top" markup="html">
					<font size="12"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[a) Removal of paraffin from freshly cut FFPE tissue sections was performed <br /><br /> <font color="blue"><b>'should'</b></font>]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="335" y="0" width="21" height="16" uuid="580a29d6-0896-47d2-92c4-c2c3618683dc"/>
				<textElement verticalAlignment="Top" markup="html">
					<font size="12"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[Yes]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<image vAlign="Top">
				<reportElement x="322" y="0" width="10" height="16" uuid="9a01e8dd-e16a-4434-8aa5-05b30872073b"/>
				<imageExpression><![CDATA["unchecked.png"]]></imageExpression>
			</image>
			<image vAlign="Top">
				<reportElement x="322" y="0" width="10" height="16" uuid="ddbef11c-44ff-4bd7-b210-e06d30d66440">
					<printWhenExpression><![CDATA[$F{ffp1_v3_684_a_v1}.trim().equalsIgnoreCase("Yes")]]></printWhenExpression>
				</reportElement>
				<imageExpression><![CDATA["checked.png"]]></imageExpression>
			</image>
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="335" y="16" width="16" height="16" uuid="e59f91f8-921e-47b7-8ffb-953a96c10bac"/>
				<textElement verticalAlignment="Top" markup="html">
					<font size="12"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[No]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<image vAlign="Top">
				<reportElement x="322" y="16" width="10" height="16" uuid="a79e29ef-01ca-4c3e-8eeb-a37112648435"/>
				<imageExpression><![CDATA["unchecked.png"]]></imageExpression>
			</image>
			<image vAlign="Top">
				<reportElement x="322" y="16" width="10" height="16" uuid="27471993-1c51-40f1-a1f6-a33f7a3744a0">
					<printWhenExpression><![CDATA[$F{ffp1_v3_684_a_v1}.trim().equalsIgnoreCase("No")]]></printWhenExpression>
				</reportElement>
				<imageExpression><![CDATA["checked.png"]]></imageExpression>
			</image>
		</band>
		<band height="78">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement positionType="Float" x="25" y="0" width="545" height="78" uuid="fa6357b4-fcd5-432c-bd05-65f3d056e937"/>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" verticalAlignment="Middle" markup="html">
					<font size="12" pdfFontName="net/sf/jasperreports/fonts/dejavu/DejaVuSerif-Italic.ttf" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[This can be done, e.g. by treating with xylene or alternatives, subsequent centrifugation, followed by washing of the resulting pellet with ethanol. Commercially available deparaffinization solutions can be used, obviating the need to pellet FFPE tissues.]]></text>
			</staticText>
		</band>
		<band height="52" splitType="Prevent">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="25" y="0" width="272" height="52" uuid="71501b1c-df69-41f8-b85c-6c6efc329a37"/>
				<textElement verticalAlignment="Top" markup="html">
					<font size="12"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[b) Sections were resuspended in lysis buffer, then digested with proteinase K <br /><br /> <font color="blue"><b>'should'</b></font>]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="335" y="0" width="21" height="16" uuid="77ba762d-835f-4a9c-b565-bc2e5afb8837"/>
				<textElement verticalAlignment="Top" markup="html">
					<font size="12"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[Yes]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<image vAlign="Top">
				<reportElement x="322" y="0" width="10" height="16" uuid="e7ac42b4-26e6-4e57-bb73-ba16d1b5903e"/>
				<imageExpression><![CDATA["unchecked.png"]]></imageExpression>
			</image>
			<image vAlign="Top">
				<reportElement x="322" y="0" width="10" height="16" uuid="c0838175-fed1-4d88-9e5b-e1c40a911d9b">
					<printWhenExpression><![CDATA[$F{ffp1_v3_684_b_v1}.trim().equalsIgnoreCase("Yes")]]></printWhenExpression>
				</reportElement>
				<imageExpression><![CDATA["checked.png"]]></imageExpression>
			</image>
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="335" y="16" width="16" height="16" uuid="a0d11423-85af-4c6e-8ce6-6ff1bdfbad73"/>
				<textElement verticalAlignment="Top" markup="html">
					<font size="12"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[No]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<image vAlign="Top">
				<reportElement x="322" y="16" width="10" height="16" uuid="3eb232db-55b9-4f62-8f09-5af19cebef0c"/>
				<imageExpression><![CDATA["unchecked.png"]]></imageExpression>
			</image>
			<image vAlign="Top">
				<reportElement x="322" y="16" width="10" height="16" uuid="f8d8e71a-175d-4b94-b898-3f50de5c1659">
					<printWhenExpression><![CDATA[$F{ffp1_v3_684_b_v1}.trim().equalsIgnoreCase("No")]]></printWhenExpression>
				</reportElement>
				<imageExpression><![CDATA["checked.png"]]></imageExpression>
			</image>
		</band>
		<band height="110">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement positionType="Float" x="25" y="0" width="545" height="110" uuid="cd9f3087-84e0-45ab-b886-cb878d2a8903"/>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" verticalAlignment="Middle" markup="html">
					<font size="12" pdfFontName="net/sf/jasperreports/fonts/dejavu/DejaVuSerif-Italic.ttf" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[Where a heating step is included into the protocol, the lysis buffer should not contain high concentrations of chaotropic salts. The combination of high concentration of chaotropic salt and elevated temperatures can lead to RNA degradation. The typical incubation duration can range from 10 min to 18 h (depending on the tissue type and size) at a temperature varying from 37-60Â°C. It is advised to optimize lysis buffer for the proteinase digestion step.]]></text>
			</staticText>
		</band>
		<band height="42" splitType="Prevent">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="25" y="0" width="272" height="42" uuid="5f3eed4f-43af-4ad1-b17a-3a5c70270ad3"/>
				<textElement verticalAlignment="Top" markup="html">
					<font size="12"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[c) RNA was extracted from lysate <br /><br /> <font color="blue"><b>'should'</b></font>]]></text>
			</staticText>
