				<textElement verticalAlignment="Top" markup="html">
					<font size="12"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[d) Interference: exogenous controls (spiked in RNA and DNA controls) were used or qPCR response curves were inspected for anomalies, or using an endogenous RNA for RT-PCR inhibition test by introducing increasing eluate volumes into the examination <br /><br /> <font color="blue"><b>'should'</b></font>]]></text>
			</staticText>
