		<band height="126">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement positionType="Float" x="25" y="0" width="545" height="126" uuid="faa6cd6b-f04f-469d-b508-115581b2a371"/>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" verticalAlignment="Middle" markup="html">
					<font size="12" pdfFontName="net/sf/jasperreports/fonts/dejavu/DejaVuSerif-Italic.ttf" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[Formalin fixation has a negative impact on RNA integrity and reliability of RNA quality measurements. Chemical modifications caused by formaldehyde cannot be reliably detected in standard quality control assays such as elecrophoretic RNA fragment length measurement, but they interfere with the enzymatic examination. Chemical modifications caused by formaldehyde are not reflected by the RIN value calculation. Therefore, measurement of the integrity alone is not sufficient to assess the usability of RNA from FFPE for quantitative RT-PCR.]]></text>
			</staticText>
		</band>
		<band height="54">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement positionType="Float" x="25" y="0" width="545" height="54" uuid="c6d9cf48-7d7e-442d-bbeb-352952f625ff"/>
				<textElement verticalAlignment="Middle" markup="html">
					<font size="14" isBold="true" pdfFontName="net/sf/jasperreports/fonts/dejavu/DejaVuSerif-Bold.ttf" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[6.10. Storage of isolated RNA<br />6.10.1. General]]></text>
			</staticText>
		</band>
		<band height="62">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement positionType="Float" x="25" y="0" width="545" height="62" uuid="02ad2a58-b501-44c0-8843-25d14ab922f4"/>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" verticalAlignment="Middle" markup="html">
					<font size="12" pdfFontName="net/sf/jasperreports/fonts/dejavu/DejaVuSerif-Italic.ttf" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[para1) For long-term storage, usually the isolated RNA is frozen. However, for RNA preservation other validated methods for archiving can also be used.]]></text>
			</staticText>
		</band>
		<band height="68" splitType="Prevent">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="25" y="0" width="272" height="68" uuid="0e11955a-15cc-4d86-bc15-5f9e37ff2079"/>
				<textElement verticalAlignment="Top" markup="html">
					<font size="12"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[para2) For long-term storage, aliquots of isolated RNA were generated to avoid repeated freezing and thawing <br /><br /> <font color="blue"><b>'should'</b></font>]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="335" y="0" width="21" height="16" uuid="d3badc8d-0079-4112-8a58-3692c18adf62"/>
